Internal documentation has been moved off this public repository.

The historical docs (EVIDENCE_AUDIT_EYE.md, EVIDENCE_AUDIT_HYDRATION.md,
ADVERSARIAL_UX_REPORT.md, DESIGN_LANGUAGE.md, REFERENCES.md, AUDIT_TRAIL.md,
VERIFICATION.md, IMPLEMENTATION_PLAN.md, milestone docs M0-M6.md) were
removed at the maintainer's request in v0.1.0.2 (commit that retains
them was force-rewritten). They are kept in the maintainer's local
working tree and any future contributor who needs access can request
it via a GitHub issue on this repository.

The audit work is preserved in the master's local repository under
the same commit SHAs as the public release (the audit commits are
referenced inline in the cited fixes inside the codebase).

If you are reviewing Rewind's evidence base for the public v0.1.0
release, see the README "More info" link and the in-app Settings →
About panel — those surfaces paraphrase the source claims and link to
canonical primary sources (Mayo Clinic, Cleveland Clinic, AOA, AAO).
